I think @Ginxo wrote about some limitation on GA side there is some bug which blocks this easier way of config
from @Ginxo`s msg:

just to let you know I tried to use matrix in order not to duplicate commands for openjdk8 and 11, but it's not possible to use it in usues like uses: kiegroup/github-action-build-chain@{{ matrix.build-chain-version}}
the limitation is already reported and there's no way of work around it (apart from duplicate it again)
The other thing you should pay attention to is workflow-file-name since the name of the flow is defined there's no way about how to get file-name information (I already reported it to github) (edited)
